{"tid":1281764,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"23億起個水上樂園，17億起條天橋係咩玩法？","createTime":"2019-07-03T11:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T02:02:49.000Z","uid":122603,"like":82,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2c864a63718e1bf9c733f0d91420b6c27ce0303b","tid":1281764,"uid":122603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:14:24.000Z","msg":"2013年2月27日，財政司司長曾俊華透過《2013年至2014年度香港政府財政預算案》表示，將會向海洋公園貸款22億9千萬港元以興建水上樂園。<br />\n有冇師兄查到實質使左幾錢去起？如果就只係23億，可以起到個阿凡達咁既水上樂園，但政府起條元朗天橋就造價17億，邊個答下我，而家個政府想點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J3GePZp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ3GePZp.gif&h=8211212e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8626f191a934630d65ffbcd79aa79beb9ae2977","tid":1281764,"uid":83251,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:30:16.000Z","msg":"世紀巨貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5498d25cdecc1ad9c49f32184830d16f7a28c2","tid":1281764,"uid":240973,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T15:55:08.000Z","msg":"行政費用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81daedcbd5828afd7617b44c91699b80c4df9505","tid":1281764,"uid":123587,"like":2,"dislike":84,"score":-82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"你睇下5年工資物價升左幾多<br />\n加上地質環境完全唔同<br />\n你係市區同荒地起野成本都唔阿"},{"pid":"eb1d1e868cd56a8cb8cfd90900887fd1b7cf57dd","tid":1281764,"uid":83251,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"81daedcbd5828afd7617b44c91699b80c4df9505","tid":1281764,"uid":123587,"like":2,"dislike":84,"score":-82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"你睇下5年工資物價升左幾多<br />\n加上地質環境完全唔同<br />\n你係市區同荒地起野成本都唔阿"},"