islike":84,"score":-82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"你睇下5年工資物價升左幾多<br />\n加上地質環境完全唔同<br />\n你係市區同荒地起野成本都唔阿"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:01:42.000Z","msg":"既然唔Cost Effective 點解仲要堅持起？"},{"pid":"c54406dae1311349b996449eefc7a17ac8258f8b","tid":1281764,"uid":236646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"元朗條橋起完唔止17億啦.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />起碼20億以上<br />\n<br />\n元朗個個地段本身好似話有榕洞....要打地基真係好會好鬼貴...仲要咁深<br />\n我諗本身就唔貴, 但係呢個價一定食唔少水啦。<br />\n人地三十億可以起五棟居屋加兩層停車場再加一個大花園.....<br />\n成個小屋苑都起到。仲要連埋地基<br />\n<br />\n你17億拎黎起條作用不大的橋.....紋晒身大家都知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要拒絕左幾次都繼續上馬.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時中左標睇下邊間承建商囉...我估都係中資...<br />\n然後下面D SUB CON 係邊個邊個D人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b26880366329bf92b51ff52336ffe1064617ca","tid":1281764,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81daedcbd5828afd7617b44c91699b80c4df9505","tid":1281764,"uid":123587,"like":2,"dislike":84,"score":-82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"你睇下5年工資物價升左幾多<br />\n加上地質環境完全唔同<br />\n你係市區同荒地起野成本都唔阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:10:49.000Z","msg":"用下個腦<br />\n不過可能你冇sorry"},{"pid":"4c66fbe4eb7d08eb20cbb29531ef966a83924141","tid":1281764,"uid":94739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9aaa5a8fc7f5719fd00248b8573986fd8afe3d5","tid":1281764,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ebdb23