根本唔需要起天橋<br />\n仲用17億根本痴線<br />\n<br />\n佢起天橋係因為個到起左新樓 想直接有路駁出去大馬路 方便幫棟樓升樓價<br />\n個棟樓本身位置係水務署<br />\n有日無啦啦開始拆<br />\n連帶格離個公眾垃圾房都搬位搬到對正格離個幼稚園(佢地有抗議,但當然被無視)<br />\n<br />\n最後原來就係因為要比地產商去起樓"},{"pid":"64adbd649d3e8c708dc276714ebac9f035219ae4","tid":1281764,"uid":118350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:24:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c3ceaae4aed5f32ab34a446f58ad74959093c7a8","tid":1281764,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4130135941d39dc4e99ce62c77396d159d1d11c9","tid":1281764,"uid":137694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb1d1e868cd56a8cb8cfd90900887fd1b7cf57dd","tid":1281764,"uid":83251,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"81daedcbd5828afd7617b44c91699b80c4df9505","tid":1281764,"uid":123587,"like":2,"dislike":84,"score":-82,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T16:07:01.000Z","msg":"你睇下5年工資物價升左幾多<br />\n加上地質環境完全唔同<br />\n你係市區同荒地起野成本都唔阿"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"貪就貪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"其實咁樣屈有意義咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搞掂眼前問題先理依啲野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}